  <title>Playback Controls</title>

  <p>Learn how to play back your recordings individually or all together.</p>

  <section id="individual-playback">
    <title>Playing Individual Tracks</title>
    <list>
      <item><p>Click the <gui style="button">‚ñ∂</gui> (play) button on a track to start playing.</p></item>
      <item><p>The button changes to <gui style="button">‚è∏</gui> (pause) while playing.</p></item>
      <item><p>Click again to pause playback.</p></item>
      <item><p>Click again to resume from where you paused.</p></item>
    </list>
    <p>When playback reaches the end of the track, it automatically stops 
    and resets to the beginning.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="global-playback">
    <title>Playing All Tracks</title>
    <p>Global playback controls are in the header bar:</p>
    
    <terms>
      <item>
        <title><gui style="button">‚ñ∂ Play All</gui> (<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Space</key></keyseq>)</title>
        <p>Starts all tracks with recordings simultaneously. All tracks play 
        in sync, allowing you to hear how they sound together.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
        <title><gui style="button">‚è∏ Pause All</gui> (<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Space</key></keyseq>)</title>
        <p>When tracks are playing, the button changes to pause. Click to 
        pause all tracks, preserving their positions.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
        <title><gui style="button">‚èπ Stop All</gui> (<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>.</key></keyseq>)</title>
        <p>Stops all playback immediately and resets all tracks to the beginning.</p>
      </item>
    </terms>
  </section>

  <section id="pause-resume">
    <title>Pause and Resume</title>
    <p><app>Audio Recorder</app> supports true pause/resume functionality:</p>
    <list>
      <item><p>When you pause a track, its position is preserved.</p></item>
      <item><p>Resuming continues from exactly where you paused.</p></item>
      <item><p>Use <gui style="button">Stop All</gui> to reset all tracks to the beginning.</p></item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section id="mixing-preview">
    <title>Previewing Your Mix</title>
    <p>To hear how your tracks sound together:</p>
    <steps>
      <item><p>Mute any tracks you want to exclude by clicking their 
      <gui style="button">üîä</gui> buttons.</p></item>
      <item><p>Press <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Space</key></keyseq> to play all tracks.</p></item>
      <item><p>Adjust which tracks are muted to find the right balance.</p></item>
    </steps>
  </section>

